<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style type="text/css">
      body#welcome h1, body#meeting h1 {
        font-family: 'times new roman', serif;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0px; }
      body#welcome p, body#meeting p {
        margin: 15px 0px; }
      body#welcome div.section-title, body#welcome strong, body#meeting div.section-title, body#meeting strong {
        font-family: arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: bold; }
      body#welcome div.post-script, body#meeting div.post-script {
        color: #999999;
        margin-top: 40px; }
      body#welcome div.post-script ul, body#meeting div.post-script ul {
        margin-top: 10px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body id="meeting">
    <h1>S'UP at <%= ENV['COMPANY_NAME'] %> these days with <%= "#{@members[0]}, #{@members[1]}, and #{@members[2]}?" %></h1>
    <p>
      Find a time that works between now and Friday, and put a quick 20-min break on the calendar. Then get together and fill each other in on something you're focused on these days.
    </p>
    <p>
      How about <%= @times.first.strftime("%A, %B %d") %>? <strong><%= @meeting.leader %>, you're in charge this week to make it happen!</strong>
    </p>

    <p class="signature">Team love,
      <br>
      <%= ENV['COMPANY_NAME'] %>
    </p>

  </body>
</html>